New features beyond ADIOS:

For Writing:
1. Ability to annotate data utility
2. Ability to write multiple blocks for a single var during a single output
3. Specify output time deadlines
4. relate variables to be treated as units for storage locality

For Reading:
1. Specify hard deadline and desired deadlines
2. Specify quality acceptability and reporting delivered quality
3. Identify which data read is of what quality level
4. Specify desired ultimate data set to be read and request performance caching
